          </a></li>
          <li><a class="metric-card" href="#11">
            <span class="metric-label">Stability</span>
            <h3>Instability &amp; abstractness</h3>
            <p>Plot packages on the distance-from-main-sequence diagram to find which ones are in the zone of pain.</p>
          </a></li>
